# Shared Project Conventions

Place this file at the parent of your project directories (e.g., ~/projects/CLAUDE.md).
It will be loaded for every project underneath.

## Conventions

- Planning/roadmap file goes in `TODO.md` at the project root — living document for phases, tasks, and status
- Use conventional commits: `feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`, `chore:`, `refactor:`, `test:`
- All projects should have a README.md with setup instructions
- Never commit secrets, API keys, or `.env` files
